welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Rancho San Diego, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and discover all that this wonderful place has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gillespie Field Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

wifi.note: Wifi access is limited to the main terminal only.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Terminal 2

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
